title: Proprietors' and Rental Income for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Varibbles--(1)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1929-1946 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1945-1966. These Figures Are Monthly Totals At Annual Rates. Source: Survey Of Current Business, Supplement: National Income, 1954 Edition, For Datathrough 1945; 1946 Data Are From The July, 1958 Issue Of Survey Of Current Business.
